column16: Dee Gordon lines out, pitcher Jerry Blevins to first baseman Lucas Duda.   Adeiny Hechavarria to 2nd.
Ichiro Suzuki lines out softly to first baseman Lucas Duda.
Christian Yelich grounds out, second baseman Daniel Murphy to first baseman Lucas Duda.
Dee Gordon grounds out, shortstop Wilmer Flores to first baseman Lucas Duda.
Jeff Baker lines out to center fielder Juan Lagares.
Christian Yelich grounds into a double play, shortstop Wilmer Flores to second baseman Daniel Murphy to first baseman Lucas Duda.   Dee Gordon out at 2nd.

Marlins challenged (tag play), call on the field was overturned: Dee Gordon reaches on a fielder's choice, fielded by second baseman Daniel Murphy.   Ichiro Suzuki scores.  Throwing error by second baseman Daniel Murphy.
Chase Utley grounds out to first baseman Lucas Duda.
Odubel Herrera flies out to center fielder Juan Lagares.
A.  J.   Pierzynski grounds out, second baseman Ruben Tejada to first baseman Lucas Duda.
Nick Markakis called out on strikes.
Bryce Harper lines out to right fielder Curtis Granderson.
